Dialogs.Dialog: 姉ヶ崎
Hey, wake up.
Um... Just a little bit...
You're gonna be late.
Only a little bit...
Geez... Your girlfriend is waking you up. Do you intend to keep sleeping？
Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！？ W-Why are you in my room！？
Hey, I already told you. I'm here to wake you up.
Is that so？ Whoa, you saw me in my pajamas.
Isn't it too late to say that now？ Hey, if you don't get ready, I'll be leaving, you sleepyhead.
...Okay.
Geez, you're still a kid...
姉ヶ崎
Hey, wake up.
No... Let me sleep a little more...
Wake up now. M-y d-e-a-r.
No, we can't do this... I already have ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ as my girlfriend...
...Hey, come on.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！？ You're here to wake me up？
Yeah, and I'm wondering who you were having an affair with in your dream.
My dream？ ...I can't remember it. Hahaha.
I'll listen to your excuse later.
Ahaha...
姉ヶ崎
Hey, I think it's about time you should wake up.
Hmm... Three more minutes...
You'll be late for school. Hey, wake up.
Just a little bit...
No~ W-a-k-e u-p！
Only a little bit... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲！？
I promised to wake you up in the morning. Did you forget？
Sorry... Is that so...？
Now, get out of your blanket. ...Kyaa！
What？
Hey, fix your clothes first. They're falling down.
Sorry.
(She saw me in such an embarrassing condition...)
姉ヶ崎
Hey, wake up.
Hmm... Just a little bit...
Hey, hurry and get up.
...Huh？ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... Good morning.
Yeah, good morning. Somehow... This feels as if we are a married couple...
姉ヶ崎
Hey, it's time to get up.
Hmm~ Hmm...
Geez... If you don't get up, I'll start teasing you.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... 'Morning. Whoa...！
'Morning. Hehe, hurry and get ready, otherwise, you won't have time for breakfast.
姉ヶ崎
Good morning！ Hey, wake up.
Hmm...
Hmm... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, good morning.
Hehe, look at your bed hair.
Eh！？
Geez, you're so helpless. I really have to be take care of you, huh？
姉ヶ崎
Hey, I'll be happy if you feel hungry now...
It's the lunch break. Of course, I'm hungry. But, why？
Well... Hehe... I made a lunch box today.
Could it be that... you made it for me？
My girlfriend's homemade lunch box, huh...？ I'm so impressed.
Geez... You don't have to exaggerate.
Oh, looks delicious. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is very family-oriented, huh？
You try it and let me know whether you like how it tastes, okay？
Okay, the taste is perfect. I like it with light seasonings like this.
I'm glad... I'll make it for you again, so I want to hear your opinion.
姉ヶ崎
Hello.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What's up？
Hehe, actually, I made a lunch box today.
A lunch box？ Is it for me？
I have one condition, though. You must eat it all. How's that？
Ah, it's a Japanese style lunch box. This is nice. It's homemade too.
I picked a menu that's good for your health. I wonder if you don't like it.
No way. ...Um, it's delicious. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is very good at cooking.
Hehe, it's fun to cook. I'll make some more for you later.
Okay, then.
Hehe... Ah, look！ You have to chew it properly... I have some tea too, so take your time, okay？
姉ヶ崎
Ah, you're here.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ What's up？
Hehe, here's a lunch box.
A lunch box？ Could it be that you made it for me？
Yeah, since I'm your girlfriend, this is natural, right？ Hehe.
Ah, a Japanese style lunch box.
I love Japanese food. It's simple but healthy, right？ Hey, why don't you taste it？
Simple, huh...？ Um, delicious. As I could expect from ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Hehe, I'm thinking about attending a cooking class.
You don't have to. This is already very delicious.
Really？ I'm glad. Then I'll make some more for you later.
姉ヶ崎
Here you are.
Thanks.
Today is a Japanese style lunch box.
Yay！ I really like it. I'm eating it now.
Eat a lot then.
姉ヶ崎
Here you are.
Thanks. Ah, today's menu is Japanese food？
Hehe, I'm concerned about my boyfriend's health, so Japanese food is the best choice.
Okay, I'm eating it now.
Hey, no one is going to snatch it from you, so eat slowly. Okay？
姉ヶ崎
Here you are.
Thanks. I've been waiting for this moment.
Hehe, you say something that makes me happy again. Today, I made some miso soup, too.
Oh, it smells nice. I'll hurry and taste it.
Ah, wait. Don't be hasty. It's still very hot.
姉ヶ崎
Hey, can you come this way？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What's up？
Well, I made a lunch box for you.
For me！？ I'm so happy. Can I really have it？
I hope you'll like it...
Wow, this looks wonderful. You even made some decorations too...
What do you think about its taste then？
I'll try it now... Oh, this is great. Perfect！
Hehehe. I think guys like to eat something like this.
Yes, it's delicious. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s food is very delicious.
Then I'll make some more for you later. If you have any special request, just let me know.
姉ヶ崎
Hello. You have a minute？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what's up？
Don't you know？ It's the lunch break, right？
Then do you want to eat with me？
Hehe, that's why I made a lunch box for you. What do you say？
A lunch box！？
Here you are. I tried making this Western style lunch. Do you like it？
Yes, I like it. I like it！ Thanks！ I'm eating it now.
How is it？ Delicious？
Yes, very delicious！ ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is really good at cooking.
Although I look like this, I like to cook. But I think I still have to keep practicing, right？
This is already very delicious.
If you praise me like this, I'll start stuffing you, you know？ Hehe.
姉ヶ崎
Ah, you really are here. Hehe, my guess wasn't wrong.
Eh, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ Why are you here during the lunch break？
Hehe, I have a question. I made a lunch box. Will you eat it with me？ What's your answer？
Really！？ I'll eat it. I'll eat it！
Hehe. Then here you are.
Western style lunch？ This is nice. I like it.
I know. How does it taste？ Let me know what you think.
I'm eating it now. Um, nothing to complain. It's delicious. What did you put in it？
I put so many things in there, but the most important ingredient is my love.
Eh！？
Hehe, shall I make some more for you later？ Do you have anything that you can't eat？
姉ヶ崎
Here you are.
Oh, thanks. This looks delicious...
I put my effort in it. ...How does it taste？
Um, delicious. A taste like this is like it was cooked by a professional.
I don't think it's that good. ...Anyway, I'm glad. Take you time to savor it.
姉ヶ崎
Here you are.
Thanks. Ah, Western food. Hmm...？ It looks like something that could be sold at a store.
Hehe, do you only appreciate its appearance？
Of course not. ...Yes, it's very delicious！
Hehe. No matter how many times you say this, it still sounds so flattery. Ah, something's sticking on your cheek. Geez.
姉ヶ崎
Okay, today's lunch box is my skillful Western style lunch.
You made the whole thing by yourself, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
Hehe, I picked this one as it's low in calorie and salt content. How's that？
I have to look at you differently... This is really great.
Hehe. Do you want me to feed you？
姉ヶ崎
Ah... Hey, hey.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ What's up？
W-Well... I had some time in the morning, so I prepared a lunch box.
You made it for me？
Yeah... Does this trouble you？
That's not the case. I'm really happy.
Is Chinese food okay for you？ I'm sorry if you don't like it...
It's absolutely okay. And... This looks awesome. It's like the one shown in the store.
I wonder how you'll like the taste. I tried my best with the seasonings.
Then I'll taste it... Yes, delicious！ Very delicious！
I'm glad... Then I'll make some more for you later, okay？
姉ヶ崎
Hello. How's everything going？
Eh, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ Why are you here during the lunch break？
Actually, I've made a lunch box for you.
Eh？ Really？ Yay！ I'm so happy~
...If you say too much, I won't give it to you.
Wait. Sorry, please forgive me.
Geez, since I don't want to waste my food, I'll forgive you then.
Okay, Chinese food special！
I love it, I love it. This looks good.
How about the taste？ Ah, you can tell me honestly. I won't get angry.
Oh, it's very delicious！ This is great. You should open a restaurant. It'll sell really well！
Hey, saying too much like that would make it sound like you're lying. Anyway, I'm glad you like it.
姉ヶ崎
Ah, you're here. Have you had your lunch yet？
Ah, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？ I'm about to go buy my lunch, though...
Hehe, actually, I've made a lunch box for you.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ made a lunch box for me？ Really？
Yes, let's eat together.
Wow, a Chinese lunch box. You made a lot！ I'll start eating.
How's the taste？ I tried my best. Does it taste good？
Delicious... So delicious that I feel like I don't deserve it.
If you make me feel happier than this, I could be floating. I'll make some more for you later.
姉ヶ崎
Here you are.
Oh, thanks.
You like Chinese food, right？
Yes. I'll eat it now.
Yes, please eat it. Hehe.
姉ヶ崎
Okay, today's menu is Chinese food. I packed it in an insulated box so it wouldn't get cold.
Thanks. I'll eat it now... Ouch！ Hot！
Hey, I've just told you. Wait until it cools down a bit before eating.
But this is very delicious.
If you insist, just go ahead and eat it. Ah, I made some soup, too.
姉ヶ崎
Okay, your lunch box. Today's the energy boosting Chinese food.
I'm eating it！ Yes, delicious！
Hehe. It's delicious, huh？ Then I'll try it too.
But I've already eaten ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲'s portion.
I made plenty, so how about you treat me specially for today？ Can you feed me then？
